JJ:  Please follow the conventional commits specification:
JJ:   <type>(<scope>): <subject>

JJ: Types:
JJ:   feat:     A new feature
JJ:   fix:      A bug fix
JJ:   chore:    Routine tasks like build scripts or dependency updates
JJ:   docs:     Changes to documentation only
JJ:   style:    Changes that don't affect code logic (e.g., formatting)
JJ:   refactor: Code changes that neither fix a bug nor add a feature
JJ:   test:     Adding or updating tests
JJ:   perf:     Code changes that improve performance
JJ:   ci:       Changes to CI configuration files or scripts
